---
import '../styles/global.css';
---

<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="it">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Savoy Beach Hotel & Thermal Spa | Bibione</title>
    
    <script src="https://identity.netlify.com/v1/netlify-identity-widget.js" is:inline></script>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Montserrat:wght@300;400;500;600&family=Playfair+Display:ital,wght@0,400;0,600;0,700;1,400&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
</head>
<body class="bg-[#faf9f6] text-[#2c3e50] font-sans antialiased overflow-x-hidden">

    <header class="absolute w-full z-50 py-8">
        <div class="max-w-screen-2xl mx-auto px-8 flex justify-between items-center">
            <a href="/" class="text-3xl font-bold tracking-[0.2em] text-white" style="font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;">
                SAVOY<span class="text-[#d4af37]">.</span>
            </a>
            <nav class="hidden md:flex space-x-12 text-[11px] text-white uppercase tracking-[0.3em]" style="font-family: 'Montserrat', sans-serif;">
                <a href="/camere" class="hover:text-[#d4af37] transition duration-500 relative group">
                    Camere
                    <span class="absolute -bottom-2 left-0 w-0 h-[1px] bg-[#d4af37] transition-all duration-500 group-hover:w-full"></span>
                </a>
                <a href="/spa" class="hover:text-[#d4af37] transition duration-500 relative group">
                    Spa
                    <span class="absolute -bottom-2 left-0 w-0 h-[1px] bg-[#d4af37] transition-all duration-500 group-hover:w-full"></span>
                </a>
                <a href="/ristorante" class="hover:text-[#d4af37] transition duration-500 relative group">
                    Ristorante
                    <span class="absolute -bottom-2 left-0 w-0 h-[1px] bg-[#d4af37] transition-all duration-500 group-hover:w-full"></span>
                </a>
            </nav>
            <a href="#booking" class="bg-[#d4af37] text-white px-8 py-3 text-xs uppercase tracking-[0.2em] hover:bg-white hover:text-black transition duration-500" style="font-family: 'Montserrat', sans-serif;">
                Prenota
            </a>
        </div>
    </header>

    <section class="relative h-[95vh] flex items-end pb-24 justify-center">
        <div class="absolute inset-0 z-0">
            <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1540541338287-41700207dee6?ixlib=rb-4.0.3&auto=format&fit=crop&w=1920&q=80" alt="Savoy" class="w-full h-full object-cover" />
            <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-t from-black/90 via-black/20 to-black/40"></div>
        </div>

        <div class="relative z-10 text-center px-4 max-w-4xl mx-auto mt-32">
            <h1 class="text-5xl md:text-8xl text-white font-light leading-none mb-6" style="font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;">
                Oltre il <span class="italic text-[#d4af37]">Lusso</span>.
            </h1>
            <p class="text-white/80 text-xs md:text-sm font-light tracking-[0.3em] uppercase" style="font-family: 'Montserrat', sans-serif;">
                Bibione Thermae & Resort
            </p>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section class="py-32 max-w-screen-xl mx-auto px-6">
        
        <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row items-center gap-12 mb-32">
            <div class="md:w-7/12 relative group overflow-hidden">
                <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1611892440504-42a792e24d32?ixlib=rb-4.0.3&auto=format&fit=crop&w=1200&q=80" alt="Suite" class="w-full h-[80vh] object-cover transition duration-1000 group-hover:scale-105">
            </div>
            <div class="md:w-5/12 md:-ml-24 relative z-10 bg-[#faf9f6] p-12 md:p-16 shadow-2xl">
                <p class="text-[#d4af37] text-xs uppercase tracking-[0.3em] mb-4 font-semibold" style="font-family: 'Montserrat', sans-serif;">01. L'Ospitalità</p>
                <h2 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl mb-6 text-[#1a1a1a]" style="font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;">Suite & Camere</h2>
                <p class="text-gray-500 font-light leading-loose mb-10">Ogni dettaglio è pensato per elevare il tuo riposo. Scegli tra ampie vetrate vista mare o rifugi intimi dal design contemporaneo.</p>
                <a href="/camere" class="inline-flex items-center text-xs uppercase tracking-[0.2em] font-medium group" style="font-family: 'Montserrat', sans-serif;">Scopri le tipologie <span class="ml-4 w-12 h-[1px] bg-black group-hover:w-24 transition-all duration-500"></span></a>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row-reverse items-center gap-12 mb-32">
            <div class="md:w-7/12 relative group overflow-hidden">
                <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1544161515-4ab6ce6db874?ixlib=rb-4.0.3&auto=format&fit=crop&w=1200&q=80" alt="Spa" class="w-full h-[80vh] object-cover transition duration-1000 group-hover:scale-105">
            </div>
            <div class="md:w-5/12 md:-mr-24 relative z-10 bg-[#0f172a] text-white p-12 md:p-16 shadow-2xl">
                <p class="text-[#d4af37] text-xs uppercase tracking-[0.3em] mb-4 font-semibold" style="font-family: 'Montserrat', sans-serif;">02. Il Benessere</p>
                <h2 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl mb-6" style="font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;">Thermal Spa</h2>
                <p class="text-gray-400 font-light leading-loose mb-10">Un tunnel sotterraneo riscaldato ti collega direttamente a Bibione Thermae. Raggiungi le piscine termali comodamente in accappatoio dalla tua camera.</p>
                <a href="/spa" class="inline-flex items-center text-xs uppercase tracking-[0.2em] font-medium group text-white hover:text-[#d4af37] transition duration-300" style="font-family: 'Montserrat', sans-serif;">Esplora i trattamenti <span class="ml-4 w-12 h-[1px] bg-white group-hover:bg-[#d4af37] group-hover:w-24 transition-all duration-500"></span></a>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row items-center gap-12">
            <div class="md:w-7/12 relative group overflow-hidden">
                <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1514362545857-3bc16c4c7d1b?ixlib=rb-4.0.3&auto=format&fit=crop&w=1200&q=80" alt="Ristorante" class="w-full h-[80vh] object-cover transition duration-1000 group-hover:scale-105">
            </div>
            <div class="md:w-5/12 md:-ml-24 relative z-10 bg-[#faf9f6] p-12 md:p-16 shadow-2xl">
                <p class="text-[#d4af37] text-xs uppercase tracking-[0.3em] mb-4 font-semibold" style="font-family: 'Montserrat', sans-serif;">03. Il Gusto</p>
                <h2 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl mb-6 text-[#1a1a1a]" style="font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;">Duca d'Aosta</h2>
                <p class="text-gray-500 font-light leading-loose mb-10">Un'esperienza culinaria d'eccellenza. Il nostro ristorante gourmet offre sapori autentici accompagnati dalle migliori etichette della nostra cantina privata.</p>
                <a href="/ristorante" class="inline-flex items-center text-xs uppercase tracking-[0.2em] font-medium group" style="font-family: 'Montserrat', sans-serif;">Scopri il menù <span class="ml-4 w-12 h-[1px] bg-black group-hover:w-24 transition-all duration-500"></span></a>
            </div>
        </div>

    </section>

    <footer class="bg-[#0f172a] text-white pt-24 pb-12 border-t border-gray-800">
        <div class="max-w-screen-xl mx-auto px-6 grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-16 mb-16">
            
            <div>
                <a href="/" class="text-3xl font-bold tracking-[0.2em] text-white mb-8 block" style="font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;">
                    SAVOY<span class="text-[#d4af37]">.</span>
                </a>
                <p class="text-gray-400 font-light leading-loose mb-6 text-sm">
                    Un'oasi a 5 stelle aperta tutto l'anno. Il tuo rifugio di lusso fronte mare a Bibione, direttamente collegato al centro termale.
                </p>
            </div>

            <div>
                <h4 class="text-[#d4af37] text-xs uppercase tracking-[0.3em] font-semibold mb-6" style="font-family: 'Montserrat', sans-serif;">Contatti</h4>
                <ul class="text-gray-400 font-light text-sm space-y-4">
                    <li>📍 Corso Europa, 51 - 30028 Bibione (VE)</li>
                    <li>📞 +39 0431 430144</li>
                    <li>✉️ hotel@etgroup.info</li>
                </ul>
            </div>

            <div>
                <h4 class="text-[#d4af37] text-xs uppercase tracking-[0.3em] font-semibold mb-6" style="font-family: 'Montserrat', sans-serif;">Esplora</h4>
                <ul class="text-gray-400 font-light text-sm space-y-4">
                    <li><a href="/camere" class="hover:text-white transition">Camere & Suite</a></li>
                    <li><a href="/spa" class="hover:text-white transition">Thermal Spa</a></li>
                    <li><a href="/ristorante" class="hover:text-white transition">Ristorante Duca d'Aosta</a></li>
                    <li><a href="/admin/" class="hover:text-white transition">Pannello Direzione (CMS)</a></li>
                </ul>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="max-w-screen-xl mx-auto px-6 text-center text-gray-600 text-xs border-t border-gray-800 pt-8" style="font-family: 'Montserrat', sans-serif;">
            &copy; 2026 Savoy Beach Hotel & Thermal Spa. Tutti i diritti riservati.
        </div>
    </footer>

</body>
</html>